<h1><b>Taxi Reservation Confirmation</b></h1>

Hello, <b><%= @user.name %></b>

<p>
  The reservation of the taxi is scheduled for <b><%= @reservation.service_begin.strftime("%d/%m/%Y at %H:%M") %></b> at
  the place of departure <b><%= @reservation.pick_up_location %></b>,<b> <%= @reservation.city %> </b>and the final
  destination is
  <b><%= @reservation.drop_off_location %></b>.
</p>
<% unless @reservation.round_trip %>
    <p>
      The return is scheduled for the <b><%= @reservation.service_end.strftime("%d/%m/%Y at %H:%M") %> </b>
      at the final destination mentioned above.
    </p>
<% end %>
<p>
  The price to be paid to the driver will be <b>
  <%= number_to_currency @reservation.final_price, precision: 2, unit: 'â‚¬', separator: ',', delimiter: '.', format: '%n%u' %></b>,
  which include luggage according to the taxi selected.
  <% unless @reservation.special_request.nil? %>
      Your special request is :<b><%= @reservation.special_request %></b>
  <% end %>
</p>

<p>
  For further questions contact the Setare team through the provided contact.
</p>
<p>Thank you for choosing,</p>
